<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#05389db03419464110b9d8e574908df8>.
<#05389db03419464110b9d8e574908df8> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://statistikdatabasen.scb.se/dataset/TAB3149>;
