<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#28ec944883d52c532908aa1897436c75>.
<#28ec944883d52c532908aa1897436c75> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://catalog.gavle.se/store/1/resource/296>;
